channel.title: ::pure command
channel.description: I need a pure command for my 718, its just like a master command but gets the following skills up: str, attack, defence, range, magic, prayer, summoning, hp. Thank you.

item.title: ::pure command
item.dc:creator: @CoderOops CoderOops
item.description:
@CoderOops wrote:

1:Search your ::master command
2:Copy it
3:Change the ::master to ::pure
4:Delete those level xp adds, which u dont want (simply delete code lines)
5:After you have done that, compile
6: Enjoy.
